B: â€œThatâ€™s it!â€<br />
C: â€œJesus, youâ€™re really weird, what about you, what do you <em>feel</em>, huh? Do you jack off, or jerk off, or whatever you call it?â€<br />
B: â€œWhat do you think?â€<br />
C: â€œWhat do I think? I think youâ€™re married to a fat lady and you go home and <em>fuck the living daylights out of her</em>!!â€<br />
B: â€œSounds good to me.â€</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Conrad exhales deeply and lies down on the couch; relief and surprise mix in his face. Pleased, Berger stands over him.</p>

<p>â€œLittle advice about feeling, kiddo. Donâ€™t expect it always to tickle.â€</p>

